     F** AB#RFA ************************************************
     F*  PRINT PICK-UP LIST (PALLETE LIST FRREZED)             *
     F*  N.HYOTO 01.05.11                                      *
     F*  H.AMANO 01.11.30   CHECK RELEASE DATE                 *
     F*  H.AMANO 02.04.12   CHG LOGIC WHEN THERE IS ONLY ONE   *
     F*                     S LABEL AND CHANGED QTY.           *
     F*  H.AMANO 02.05.16   OMIT DELETE DATA IN AB#PP10        *
     F*  H.AMANO 02.05.22   ADD PALLET#                        *
     F*  H.AMANO 02.06.10   CHECK DELIVERY CODE                *
     F*        NOT 5150 --> CHANGE PALLET BY PART
     F*  H.AMANO 02.08.12   5172 -> PART/PALLET                *
     F*  H.AMANO 02.10.23   INCREASE -> UPDATE FCRQTY          *
     F*  H.AMANO 03.02.12   5148 -> PART/PALLET                *
     F*  H.AMANO 03.02.12   ALL                                *
     F*  H.AMANO 04.04.27   ADD WORK FILE FOR MIXED PALLET SHEET
     F*  H.AMANO 04.12.01   5191 -> PART/PALLET                *
     F*  H.AMANO 04.12.10   5196, 9197 --> PART/PALLET         *
     F*  TCHK1   04/13/06   BUG FIX
