     F*  TCHK8   02/12/13   ADD 5157 --> PART/PALLET
     F*  TCHK9   07/17/14   ADD 5150 --> PART/PALLET
     F*  TCHKA   01/20/15   ADD 5185 --> PART/PALLET
JW1  F*  JW      01/23/17   ADD 22 DELEVERY CODES FOR PART/PALLET
JW2  F*  JW      04/26/17   ADD 5165 --> PART/PALLET
JW3  F*  JW      08/15/17   ADD 5228 --> PART/PALLET
JW3  F*  JW      08/31/17   ADD 5230 --> PART/PALLET
JW4  F*  JW      09/18/17   ADD 5108 --> PART/PALLET
JW4  F*                     ADD EDIPP42 (PART/PALLET MASTER)
