TCHK1C                     KFLD           PNOBI            SHIP BIN
TCHK1C                     KFLD           K21              RELEASE YY
TCHK1C                     KFLD           K22                      MM
TCHK1C                     KFLD           K23                      DD
TCHK1C                     KFLD           BANONY           DELIVERY
TCHK1C                     KFLD           BANUKE           FACTORY
TCHK1C                     KFLD           BASHIN           I PART
TCHK1C                     KFLD           W@SEQ#  60
      * ABF4P01
     C           KEY3      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           WNONY            DELIVERY
     C                     KFLD           PNUKE            DOCK
     C                     KFLD           PNOHZ            SHIP DATE
     C                     KFLD           PNOBI            BIN
     C                     KFLD           K21              RELEASED YY
     C                     KFLD           K22
     C                     KFLD           K23
     C*
      * ABF6L06
     C           KEY4      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           PNOHZ            SHIP DATE
     C                     KFLD           PNOBI            SHIP BIN
